HORROR ZOMBIES FROM THE CRYPT:

        Hold down 'M' and '.' for infinate lives.

        Type "CHEATMODE" during play and then 'F10' to skip levels.

        Enter " CUSTODES" for the password (don't forget the space before
        the word) to enable the level skip.  Press 'F10 to skip levels.

                                 (LEVEL CODES)

                2-"WOLFMAN"      4----"LUGOSI"      6-----"GARLIC"
                3--"HAMMER"      5-"NOSFERATU"      7-"BOGEYEATER"
                                 8--"CUSTODES"
